Via @russellbrunson

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5 REMINDERS FOR AN OVERTHINKER Presented by @incomefact ©2021 Via: @investinggoal'.
Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Remember... the more energy you give to irrational thoughts, the bigger and more serious they feel.'.
Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2. Perspective is everthing. Ask yourself if this will matter next week, next month, or next year.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. Many of the things we over-think don't end up happening. It's hard in the moment but don't let things that are unlikely to happen consume you.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4. You're allowed to ask someone if you've upset them. It might feel hard but it'll save you hours of over- thinking and talking to someone about it will help you get clarity.'.
Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. Remember that you're not alone... and many people struggle with over-thinking.'.
Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'if this has Drop a" helped you out!'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7 Things most people take a lifetime to learn.. Presented by @incomefact Via @russellbrunson 2021'.
Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Feeling sad after making a decision doesn't mean it was the wrong decision'.
Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2. Self-awareness is realizing that there is no opponent... you're fighting against yourself.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. Sometimes saying "goodbye" doesn't mean you don't love something, it just means you love yourself too.'.
Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'The lesson you struggle with will repeat itself until you learn from it.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. Ifyou keep one hand on your past and one hand on your future, you'll never have either. To embrace tomorrow, you must let go of yesterday.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6. You never know how valuable your health is until you're fighting for it, so fight for it now before you have to.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7. Your journey starts and ends entirely inside your mind. No matter where you end up, no matter how rich, pretty, famous or successful you become, you won't enjoy any of it if you get them at the expense of your mental health.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 05, 2021. node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 04, 2021 tagging @investinggoal. May be an image of text that says '8 Tips to Achieve Anything You Want in Life Presented by @incomefact ©2021 Written by Inga Stasiulionyte (success.com)'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Focus on commitment, not motivation. Just how committed are you to your goal? How important is it for you, and what are you willing to sacrifice in order to achieve it? If you find yourself fully committed, motivation will follow.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2. Seek knowledge, not results. If you focus on the excitement of discovery, improving, exploring and experimenting, your motivation will always be fueled. If you focus only on results, your motivation will be like weather it will die the minute you hit a storm. So the key is to focus on the journey, not the destination. Keep thinking about what you are learning along the way and what you can improve.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. Make the journey fun. Û It's an you make it serious, there's a big chance it will start carrying a heavy emotional weight and you will lose perspective and become stuck again.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4. Get rid of stagnating thoughts. Thoughts influence feelings and feelings determine how you view your work. You have a lot of thoughts in your head, and you always have a choice of which ones to focus on: the ones that will make you emotionally stuck (fears, doubts) or the ones that will move you forward (excitement, experimenting, trying new things, stepping out of your comfort zone).'.
Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6. Stop being nice to yourself. Motivation means action and action brings results. Sometimes your actions fail to bring the results you want. So you prefer to be nice to yourself and not put yourself in a difficult situation. You wait for the perfect timing, for an opportunity, while you drive yourself into stagnation and sometimes even into depression. Get out there, challenge yourself do something that you want to do even if you are afraid.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7. Get rid of distractions. Meaningless things and distractions will always be in your way, especially those easy, usual things you would rather do instead of focusing on new challenging and meaningful projects. Learn to focus on what is the most important. Write a list of time- wasters and hold yourself accountable to not do them.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says '8. Don't rely on others. You should never expect others to do it for you, not even your partner, friend or boss. They are all busy with their own needs. No one will make you happy or achieve your goals for you. It's all on you.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 04, 2021. node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7 signs you are born to be an Presented by @incomefact ©2021 Via @nickejtan Entrepreneur'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. You are ambitious risk taker. You want to achieve big goals in life. Your family and friends may not understand you, but you have to keep going.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says '2. You are a problem solver. Find solutions to problems in society. The bigger the problems you solve, the more money you are going to make as a consequence.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says '3. You want to make an impact in the world. You are not here just for the money, your aim is to impact and transform people's lives. You prefer working for yourself rather than working for your boss.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4. You have a small circle. Remember, you you are the average of the five people you spend the most time with. Choose your company wisely.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says '5. You invest in yourself consistenly. Investing in courses, books, seminars & mentorship is the fastest way to grow your busines and your mindset'.
Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says '6. You are a Leader. Lead and inspire people with your vision and success.'.

Photo by Business | Entrepreneurship on September 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7. You never give up. Whatever obstacles are you facing. You will always find a way to go forward and reach your goals. Winners are the ones who never give up'.
